description: As newlyweds Archie and Valerie settle into married life, they quit their respective groups, The Archies and The Pussycats, and focus on what matters. Teaching at a music school while starring in their own reality show, the happy couple can finally spend time together off the road. As Archie and Valerie make their own music together what kind of new changes in their former bands can we expect to see? Music aside, the biggest life altering event of the young couple's lives is on the horizon as Valerie announces she's pregnant! How will the family dynamic change the musical duo?
name: Archie Marries Valerie, Part 3 of 4: A Star is Born
